Running a CPP program is quite easy.
You just need  to follow these steps.
1. Install a Compiler on your machine
2. Create your program.
3. Compile yoour program and run it.

There are various IDEs that provide you editor along with terminals. Some of the most common ones are:
VSCode
Sublime Text
Notepad++
JetBrains

You can also use various online tools to do your work like 
Repl.it
CodeChef Compiler
Hackerrank Compiler
